<h2>Hello <%= @user.first_name %>,</h2>

<p>Your <strong><%= @fund.fund_type %></strong> request of <strong><%= number_to_currency(@fund.amount) %></strong> has been <strong>approved</strong>.</p>

<% if @fund.deposit? %>
  <p>The amount has been successfully added to your account balance.</p>
<% else %>
  <p>The amount has been deducted from your account balance.</p>
<% end %>

<p>You can log in to your account to view the updated balance and transaction history.</p>

<p>Thanks,<br>Broker Joke Team</p>
